{
  "schemaVersion": "1.0",
  "id": "nasty-neve-3btn",
  "label": "Nasty Neve 3-Button",
  "_doc": [
    "Neve-flavored 3-button compressor — VOCAL / DRUMS / GLUE.",
    "Mirrors Nasty3btn's UX (no knob-twiddling, gain-matched presets,",
    "single TRIM knob for taste) but with Neve-style ballistics:",
    "  - Slower attacks (Neve never sounds surgical)",
    "  - Softer knees (Neve's signature is the smooth onset)",
    "  - Lower ratios (Neve is a tone shaper more than a smasher)",
    "  - Medium-long releases (program-dependent feel without auto-release op)",
    "",
    "TOPOLOGY (same as Nasty3btn / TOY_COMP): textbook 5-op compressor.",
    "  in ─► detector ─► envelope ─► gainComputer ─► gain.gainMod (sidechain)",
    "       │                                        │",
    "       └─► gain ───────────────────────────────┴─► makeup ─► out",
    "",
    "PRESET design rationale:",
    "  VOCAL — subtle 2:1, slow 15ms attack lets vocal transients pass,",
    "          longer 350ms release for smooth sustained-vowel feel.",
    "  DRUMS — moderate 3:1 bus comp at -22 dB threshold, attack 5ms",
    "          catches snare/hat transients without crushing kick punch.",
    "  GLUE  — master-bus glue, 2.5:1 ratio with very soft 10dB knee +",
    "          long 500ms release. Catches peaks gently across whole mix."
  ],
  "canvas": { "width": 600, "height": 240 },
  "terminals": [
    { "id": "in",  "kind": "input",  "x":  40, "y": 120 },
    { "id": "out", "kind": "output", "x": 560, "y": 120 }
  ],
  "nodes": [
    { "id": "n_det",    "op": "detector",     "x": 180, "y":  60,
      "params": { "mode": "peak" } },
    { "id": "n_env",    "op": "envelope",     "x": 320, "y":  60,
      "params": { "attack": 5, "release": 200, "amount": 1, "offset": 0 } },
    { "id": "n_comp",   "op": "gainComputer", "x": 460, "y":  60,
      "params": { "thresholdDb": -22, "ratio": 3, "kneeDb": 6 } },
    { "id": "n_vca",    "op": "gain",         "x": 360, "y": 180,
      "params": { "gainDb": 0 } },
    { "id": "n_makeup", "op": "gain",         "x": 480, "y": 180,
      "params": { "gainDb": 6 } }
  ],
  "wires": [
    { "from": "in",       "to": "n_det" },
    { "from": "n_det",    "to": "n_env" },
    { "from": "n_env",    "to": "n_comp" },
    { "from": "n_comp",   "to": "n_vca.gainMod" },
    { "from": "in",       "to": "n_vca" },
    { "from": "n_vca",    "to": "n_makeup" },
    { "from": "n_makeup", "to": "out" }
  ],
  "feedback": [],
  "legendOps": ["detector", "envelope", "gainComputer", "gain"],
  "presets": [
    {
      "id": "vocal",
      "label": "VOCAL",
      "params": {
        "n_env__attack":      15,
        "n_env__release":     350,
        "n_env__amount":      1,
        "n_env__offset":      0,
        "n_comp__thresholdDb": -18,
        "n_comp__ratio":      2,
        "n_comp__kneeDb":     8,
        "n_vca__gainDb":      0,
        "n_makeup__gainDb":   3
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "drums",
      "label": "DRUMS",
      "params": {
        "n_env__attack":      5,
        "n_env__release":     200,
        "n_env__amount":      1,
        "n_env__offset":      0,
        "n_comp__thresholdDb": -22,
        "n_comp__ratio":      3,
        "n_comp__kneeDb":     6,
        "n_vca__gainDb":      0,
        "n_makeup__gainDb":   6
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "glue",
      "label": "GLUE",
      "params": {
        "n_env__attack":      8,
        "n_env__release":     500,
        "n_env__amount":      1,
        "n_env__offset":      0,
        "n_comp__thresholdDb": -16,
        "n_comp__ratio":      2.5,
        "n_comp__kneeDb":     10,
        "n_vca__gainDb":      0,
        "n_makeup__gainDb":   4
      }
    }
  ],
  "ui": {
    "mode": "presets-only",
    "defaultPreset": "drums",
    "userKnobs": [
      { "paramId": "n_makeup__gainDb", "label": "TRIM" }
    ]
  }
}
